entries.femaleVariant: Any iron I shouldn't put on my shopping list?
Iron of every caliber – feast your eyes.
Hm, well, let me think. Budget Arms is the obvious offender. Their cheap, plastic parts give them a high recoil, low range – I could go on.
If I were you, I'd watch out for Rostovic products. Firepower is unbeatable, but somehow they love to get jammed when you're in a tight spot.
Mm, I dunno... Can't really go wrong with the Satara.
